\c 21
\s Ukuzalwa kukaIsaka
\p
\v 1 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasimhambela\x + 1 Sam. 2.21.\x* uSara njengokukhuluma kwayo, njalo iN\nd kosi\nd* yenza kuSara njengoba yayitshilo\x + 17.19; 18.10,14.\x*.
\v 2 USara wasethatha isisu\x + Heb. 11.11. Gal. 4.22.\x*, wamzalela indodana uAbrahama ebudaleni bakhe, ngesikhathi esimisiweyo\x + 17.21.\x* uNkulunkulu abesitshilo kuye.
\v 3 UAbrahama wasesitha ibizo lendodana yakhe, eyazalelwa yena, uSara amzalela yona, \add wathi\add* nguIsaka\x + 17.19.\x*.
\v 4 UAbrahama wasesoka\x + Seb. 7.8.\x* uIsaka indodana yakhe isilensuku eziyisificaminwembili, njengoba uNkulunkulu wamlaya\x + 17.10,12.\x*.
\v 5 Njalo uAbrahama wayeleminyaka elikhulu\x + 17.1,17.\x* lapho ezalelwa uIsaka indodana yakhe.
\p
\v 6 USara wasesithi: UNkulunkulu ungenzele uhleko\x + Isa. 54.1. Gal. 4.27.\x*, wonke ozwayo uzahleka lami.
\v 7 Wathi futhi: Ngubani obengatsho kuAbrahama \add ukuthi\add*: USara uzamunyisa abantwana? Ngoba ngi\add m\add*zalele indodana ebudaleni bakhe\x + 18.11,12.\x*.
\s UHagari loIshmayeli basenkangala
\p
\v 8 Umntwana wakhula, walunyulwa. UAbrahama wasesenza idili elikhulu mhla uIsaka elunyulwa.
\p
\v 9 USara wasebona indodana kaHagari umGibhithekazi\x + 16.1.\x* ayeyizalele uAbrahama\x + 16.15.\x* ikloloda\x + Gal. 4.29.\x*.
\v 10 Ngakho wathi kuAbrahama: Xotsha lesisigqilikazi lendodana yaso\x + Gal. 4.30.\x*; ngoba indodana yalesisigqilikazi kayiyikudla ilifa kanye lendodana yami, kanye loIsaka.
\v 11 Lalelilizwi laba libi kakhulu emehlweni kaAbrahama, ngenxa yendodana yakhe\x + 17.18.\x*.
\v 12 Kodwa uNkulunkulu wathi kuAbrahama: Kakungabi kubi emehlweni akho, ngenxa yomfana langenxa yesigqilikazi sakho; konke uSara azakutsho kuwe, lalela ilizwi lakhe, ngoba kuIsaka inzalo yakho izabizwa\x + Roma 9.7. Heb. 11.18.\x*.
\v 13 Kodwa lendodana yesigqilikazi ngizayenza ibe yisizwe\x + 21.18; 16.10; 17.20.\x*, ngoba iyinzalo yakho.
\p
\v 14 Ngakho uAbrahama wavuka ekuseni kakhulu, wathatha isinkwa lesigxingi samanzi, wa\add ku\add*nika uHagari, e\add ku\add*beka emahlombe akhe, lomntwana, wamyekela wahamba. Wasehamba wazula enkangala iBherishebha\x + 21.31.\x*.
\v 15 Amanzi esephelile esigxingini waphosela umntwana phansi kwesinye sezihlahlakazana.
\v 16 Wasehamba wahlala phansi maqondana \add laye\add*, esuka \add kuye\add* khatshanyana, okungaba yikutshoka ngedandili; ngoba wathi: Kangingaboni ukufa komntwana. Wahlala maqondana \add laye\add*, waphakamisa ilizwi lakhe wakhala inyembezi.
\v 17 UNkulunkulu wasesizwa ilizwi lomfana. Yasimemeza ingilosi kaNkulunkulu kuHagari isemazulwini, yathi kuye: Ulani, Hagari? Ungesabi, ngoba uNkulunkulu ulizwile ilizwi lomfana lapho akhona.
\v 18 Sukuma, uphakamise umfana, umbambe ngesandla sakho; ngoba ngizamenza abe yisizwe esikhulu.
\v 19 UNkulunkulu wasevula amehlo akhe, njalo wabona umthombo wamanzi; wahamba, wagcwalisa isigxingi ngamanzi, wamnathisa umfana.
\v 20 Njalo uNkulunkulu waba lomfana\x + 39.2,3,21.\x*, wakhula, wahlala enkangala, waba ngumtshoki\x + 16.12.\x*.
\v 21 Wahlala enkangala iParani; unina wasemthathela umfazi elizweni leGibhithe\x + 24.4.\x*.
\s Isivumelwano sikaAbrahama loAbhimeleki
\p
\v 22 Kwasekusithi ngalesosikhathi uAbhimeleki loFikoli\x + 20.2; 26.1,26.\x*, induna yebutho yakhe, wakhuluma kuAbrahama wathi: UNkulunkulu ulawe kukho konke okwenzayo\x + 26.28.\x*.
\v 23 Ngakho-ke funga kimi lapha ngoNkulunkulu\x + Josh. 2.12. 1 Sam. 24.21.\x* ukuthi kawuyikungikhohlisa mina kumbe indodana yami kumbe izizukulwana zami\x + Jobe 18.19. Isa. 14.22.\x*; njengomusa engikwenzele wona, yenza kimi, lelizweni ohlala kilo njengowemzini.
\v 24 UAbrahama wasesithi: Mina ngizafunga.
\v 25 Kodwa uAbrahama wamsola uAbhimeleki ngenxa yomthombo wamanzi ebeziwuphangile izinceku zikaAbhimeleki\x + 26.15,18,20,21,22.\x*.
\v 26 UAbhimeleki wasesithi: Angazi owenze le into; njalo lawe kawungitshelanga, futhi lami kangizwanga \add ngakho\add*, ngaphandle kwalamuhla.
\v 27 UAbrahama wasethatha izimvu lenkomo, wa\add zi\add*nika uAbhimeleki; njalo bobabili benza isivumelwano\x + 26.31.\x*.
\v 28 UAbrahama wabeka amawundlukazi omhlambi ayisikhombisa wodwa.
\v 29 UAbhimeleki wasesithi kuAbrahama: Ayini lapha lamawundlukazi ayisikhombisa owabeke wodwa\x + 33.8.\x*?
\v 30 Wasesithi: Ngoba uzakwemukela esandleni sami amawundlukazi ayisikhombisa, ukuze abe yibufakazi kimi bokuthi lumthombo ngiwugebhile.
\v 31 Ngakho wabiza leyondawo\x + 21.14. 26.33.\x* \add ngokuthi\add* yiBherishebha\f + \fk iBherishebha: \fl okuyikuthi, \fq umthombo wesifungo.\f*, ngoba lapho bafunga bobabili.
\v 32 Ngakho benza isivumelwano eBherishebha. UAbhimeleki wasesukuma, loFikoli induna yebutho lakhe, babuyela elizweni lamaFilisti.
\p
\v 33 Wasehlanyela \add isihlahla\add* \w setamarisiki\w** eBherishebha wabiza khona ibizo leN\nd kosi\x + 4.26.\x*\nd*, uNkulunkulu olaphakade\x + Isa. 40.28. Roma 16.26. 1 Tim. 1.17.\x*.
\v 34 UAbrahama wasehlala njengowezizwe elizweni lamaFilisti\x + 10.14; 26.1.\x* insuku ezinengi.